OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA little haar on east coast at
OL,6,Ffirst, otherwise another dry day with
OL,7,Fsome hot or very hot spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine around, although the east
OL,9,Fcoast cooler. Mainly light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine evening with some late
OL,12,Fsunny spells. Occasional showers
OL,13,Fdevelop through the early hours,
OL,14,Fbecoming heavier and more frequent,
OL,15,Fespecially across the Lothians, with a
OL,16,Frisk of thunder, later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
