OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FRather cloudy start with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of occasionally heavy
OL,7,Fshowery rain, with a risk of thunder.
OL,8,FRain or showers turn lighter through
OL,9,Fthe afternoon with some sunny spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBright
OL,13,Fin east Saturday, otherwise rather
OL,14,Fcloudy with occasional rain, becoming
OL,15,Fpersistent later in west. Sunday and
OL,16,FMonday see sunny spells and showers
OL,17,Fwith occasionally fresh southwesterly
OL,18,Fwind. Much cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
